title: Jordan Banks Balance Sheet
description: Banks Balance Sheet in Jordan increased to 63131.90 JOD Million in September from 62859.80 JOD Million in August of 2022. Banks Balance Sheet in Jordan averaged 37238.34 JOD Million from 2002 until 2022, reaching an all time high of 63131.90 JOD Million in September of 2022 and a record low of 14248.80 JOD Million in January of 2002. This page provides - Jordan Banks Balance Sheet- actual values, historical data, forecast, chart, statistics, economic calendar and news.
author: Central Bank of Jordan
